  <div class="card">
    <h1>Heaven ðŸ’–</h1>
    <p>Every day with you feels like a dream.<br />Will you be my Valentine?</p>

    <div class="buttons">
      <button class="yes" onclick="sayYes()">Yes ðŸ’˜</button>
      <button class="no" onmouseover="moveNo(this)">No ðŸ™ƒ</button>
    </div>

    <div class="message" id="message">YAY!! ðŸ’• I love you so much ðŸ¥°</div>
